## What's Next

Day 69 begins the Monitor step — the seventh and final step of the NIST RMF. The Monitor step is where the authorization becomes a living commitment rather than a historical document. The continuous monitoring strategy built in Day 52 and updated through the implementation and assessment work now executes in earnest: GuardDuty findings reviewed daily, Config compliance checked continuously, vulnerability scans run monthly, access reviews quarterly, and the POA&M items tracked against their deadlines. The Monitor step does not end — it runs for the life of the system.

